---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="Educational disclaimer for QuizNiva lessons, quizzes, references, and practice material."
  currentPath="/disclaimer"
>
  <section class="page-intro section">
    <p class="eyebrow">Disclaimer</p>
    <h1>Educational Disclaimer</h1>
    <p>Last updated: May 26, 2026</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section prose prose--standalone">
    <h2>Learning And Practice Only</h2>
    <p>
      QuizNiva publishes educational notes, examples, MCQs, and answer explanations for self-study. The material is designed to support learning, revision, and practice, but it is not a substitute for a teacher, official syllabus, product documentation, or professional advice.
    </p>

    <h2>No Exam Or Career Guarantee</h2>
    <p>
      Completing a lesson or earning a high quiz score does not guarantee exam results, job outcomes, certification success, or admission decisions. Learners should use the quizzes as diagnostic practice and confirm important requirements with their school, exam provider, employer, or official documentation.
    </p>

    <h2>Accuracy And Corrections</h2>
    <p>
      We aim to keep explanations accurate, current, and beginner-friendly. Technology changes over time, and mistakes can happen. If you find an error, unclear wording, or an outdated reference, contact us with the page URL and the correction needed.
    </p>

    <h2>External References</h2>
    <p>
      Some lessons link to trusted external resources for further reading. Those websites are controlled by their own publishers and may change without notice. External links are included for context and do not mean QuizNiva controls or endorses every page on the linked site.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
